msgstr "卡拉格"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
msgid "I fall!"
msgstr "我失败了！"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
msgid "Oh no! Without a loremaster we cannot complete our mission!"
msgstr "噢不！没有博学者我们无法完成我们的任务！"

#. [message]: speaker=Ratheln
msgid "Aaarrgh! My students... What will become of them?"
msgstr "啊啊啊啊！我的学生……他们会怎么样？"

#. [message]: speaker=Aiglondur
msgid ""
"Without Dulcatulos to explain our actions to the Kal Karthans we’ll have to "
"fight them, too. Our mission has failed."
msgstr ""
"没有杜尔卡图洛斯来向卡尔·卡萨族人解释我们的行动，那我们就也得和他们开战。我们"
"的任务失败了。"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
msgid ""
"Without magic users from Master Perrin’s academy in your party, you can no "
"longer recruit new ones."
msgstr ""
"你的队伍中没有了来自佩林大师的学院的魔法使用者，你再也不能征募新的法师了。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
msgid "There an altar in this temple, and a staff lies upon it."
msgstr "这神庙里有一个祭坛，祭坛上摆着一根法杖。"

#. [object]: id=sorf	# Prevent it from being picked up more than once.
msgid "Staff of Righteous Flame"
msgstr "正义烈焰之杖"

#. [object]: id=sorf	# Prevent it from being picked up more than once.
msgid ""
"This staff gives a dying mage a final strike that will destroy all nearby "
"enemies."
msgstr "此法杖能让法师在临终前释放出最后一击，摧毁附近的所有敌人。"

#. [object]: id=sorf	# Prevent it from being picked up more than once.
msgid "Only a mage may wield this Staff."
msgstr "只有法师才可以使用这根法杖。"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
msgid ""
"Aaarrgh! Though I die, the flame of righteousness shall send you down to "
"darkness!"
msgstr "啊啊啊啊！ 虽然我要死了，但正义的烈焰将会送你们下地狱！"
